<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>PDF 스마트 병합 — 메이크창고</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #0e0e0e;
  --bg2: #161616;
  --bg3: #1e1e1e;
  --border: #2a2a2a;
  --border2: #383838;
  --text: #e8e8e8;
  --text2: #999;
  --text3: #555;
  --accent: #e8e8e8;
  --accent-dim: #444;
  --success: #2d6a4f;
  --success-text: #52b788;
  --error: #6b2737;
  --error-text: #f4a0b0;
  --purple: #7c6fcd;
  --teal: #2ec4b6;
  --amber: #e9a825;
  --coral: #e05c4b;
  --blue: #4a90d9;
  --green: #5aaa72;
}
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans KR', sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  min-height: 100vh;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ── Header ── */
header {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  background: rgba(14,14,14,.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 0 2rem;
  height: 56px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
}
.logo {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.logo-mark {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  background: var(--text);
  border-radius: 6px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
.logo-mark svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; fill: var(--bg); }
.logo-text {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text);
  letter-spacing: -.01em;
}
.logo-sub {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text3);
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
}
nav { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
.api-toggle {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text2);
  background: var(--bg3);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 5px 12px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all .15s;
  font-family: inherit;
}
.api-toggle:hover { border-color: var(--border2); color: var(--text); }
.api-toggle.active { border-color: var(--purple); color: var(--purple); }

/* ── API Key Panel ── */
.api-panel {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 1rem 2rem;
  display: none;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}
.api-panel.open { display: flex; }
.api-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text2); white-space: nowrap; }
.api-input {
  flex: 1;
  background: var(--bg3);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 7px 12px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  color: var(--text);
  outline: none;
  transition: border-color .15s;
}
.api-input:focus { border-color: var(--purple); }
.api-note { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text3); white-space: nowrap; }

/* ── Hero ── */
.hero {
  padding: 4rem 2rem 2.5rem;
  max-width: 860px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.hero-label {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  color: var(--purple);
  border: 1px solid var(--purple);
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  letter-spacing: .08em;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 42px);
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: -.03em;
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: .75rem;
}
.hero h1 span { color: var(--text3); }
.hero p {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--text2);
  max-width: 520px;
}

/* ── Main ── */
main {
  max-width: 860px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 2rem 4rem;
}

/* ── Drop Zone ── */
.drop-zone {
  border: 1.5px dashed var(--border2);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all .2s;
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.drop-zone:hover, .drop-zone.over {
  border-color: var(--accent-dim);
  background: var(--bg2);
}
.drop-zone input { display: none; }
.drop-icon {
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  background: var(--bg3);
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
.drop-icon svg { width: 24px; height: 24px; stroke: var(--text2); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.5; }
.drop-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: .35rem; }
.drop-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text2); }
.drop-formats {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-top: 1rem;
}
.format-pill {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  background: var(--bg3);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  color: var(--text3);
}

/* ── Section header ── */
.section-head {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.section-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  color: var(--text3);
  letter-spacing: .08em;
}
.file-count {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text2);
  background: var(--bg3);
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}

/* ── Thumb Grid ── */
.thumb-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(110px, 1fr));
  gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.thumb-card {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
  transition: border-color .15s;
}
.thumb-card:hover { border-color: var(--border2); }
.thumb-preview {
  width: 100%;
  aspect-ratio: 3/4;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--bg3);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
.thumb-preview canvas,
.thumb-preview img {
  width: 100% !important;
  height: auto !important;
  display: block;
}
.thumb-preview-empty {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  color: var(--text3);
}
.thumb-preview-empty svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 1.5; }
.thumb-preview-empty span { font-size: 10px; }
.thumb-name {
  font-size: 10px;
  padding: 5px 7px;
  color: var(--text2);
  white-space: nowrap;
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
  background: var(--bg2);
}
.thumb-remove {
  position: absolute;
  top: 5px;
  right: 5px;
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,.7);
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  color: var(--text2);
  font-size: 12px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity .15s;
  line-height: 1;
}
.thumb-card:hover .thumb-remove { opacity: 1; }
.thumb-remove:hover { color: var(--text); background: rgba(0,0,0,.9); }

/* ── Action Bar ── */
.action-bar {
  display: flex;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 7px;
  padding: 9px 18px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  background: transparent;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: inherit;
  transition: all .15s;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.btn:hover { background: var(--bg3); }
.btn:disabled { opacity: .35; cursor: not-allowed; }
.btn svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 1.8; }
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--text);
  color: var(--bg);
  border-color: transparent;
}
.btn-primary:hover { opacity: .88; background: var(--text); }
.btn-primary svg { stroke: var(--bg); }
.btn-ghost { border-color: var(--border); color: var(--text2); }
.btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--text); }

/* ── Status ── */
.status-bar {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: .75rem 1rem;
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.status-dot {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--text3);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.status-dot.active { background: var(--purple); animation: pulse 1s infinite; }
.status-dot.done { background: var(--success-text); }
.status-dot.error { background: var(--error-text); }
@keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:.4} }
.status-text { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text2); flex: 1; }
.status-progress {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  color: var(--text3);
}
.progress-track {
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--bg3);
  border-radius: 2px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.progress-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--purple);
  border-radius: 2px;
  transition: width .4s ease;
}

/* ── Group Blocks ── */
.groups-container { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.group-block {
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 10px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.group-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  background: var(--bg2);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  cursor: pointer;
  user-select: none;
}
.group-header:hover { background: var(--bg3); }
.group-index {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.gi-0 { background: rgba(124,111,205,.15); color: var(--purple); }
.gi-1 { background: rgba(46,196,182,.15); color: var(--teal); }
.gi-2 { background: rgba(233,168,37,.15); color: var(--amber); }
.gi-3 { background: rgba(224,92,75,.15); color: var(--coral); }
.gi-4 { background: rgba(74,144,217,.15); color: var(--blue); }
.gi-5 { background: rgba(90,170,114,.15); color: var(--green); }
.group-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; }
.group-meta { margin-left: auto; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text3); font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; }
.group-chevron { color: var(--text3); transition: transform .2s; }
.group-chevron svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 2; }
.group-chevron.open { transform: rotate(180deg); }
.group-body {
  padding: 12px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(90px, 1fr));
  gap: 8px;
}
.group-body.collapsed { display: none; }

/* ── Download Section ── */
.download-section {
  padding: 1.5rem;
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 1rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.download-info { }
.download-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: .2rem; }
.download-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text2); }

/* ── Footer ── */
footer {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--text3);
}
footer a { color: var(--text3); text-decoration: none; }
footer a:hover { color: var(--text2); }

/* ── Responsive ── */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  header { padding: 0 1rem; }
  .hero { padding: 2.5rem 1rem 1.5rem; }
  main { padding: 0 1rem 3rem; }
  .api-panel { padding: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .drop-zone { padding: 2.5rem 1rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <a class="logo" href="#">
    <div class="logo-mark">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M2 4h12v9H2zM5 4V2h6v2M6 8h4M6 11h2"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="logo-text">PDF 스마트 병합</div>
      <div class="logo-sub">makemine.tools</div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <nav>
    <button class="api-toggle" id="apiToggle" onclick="toggleApiPanel()">AI 설정</button>
  </nav>
</header>

<div class="api-panel" id="apiPanel">
  <span class="api-label">Anthropic API Key</span>
  <input class="api-input" type="password" id="apiKeyInput" placeholder="sk-ant-..." autocomplete="off">
  <span class="api-note">브라우저 메모리에만 저장 · 서버 전송 없음</span>
</div>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-label">SMART PDF MERGE</div>
  <h1>여러 PDF를 한 번에<br><span>자동 분류 후 병합</span></h1>
  <p>AI가 첫 페이지 레이아웃과 파일명을 분석해 같은 종류끼리 묶고 순서대로 병합합니다.</p>
</section>

<main>
  <!-- Drop Zone -->
  <div class="drop-zone" id="dropZone" onclick="document.getElementById('fileInput').click()">
    <input type="file" id="fileInput" multiple accept=".pdf">
    <div class="drop-icon">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M17 8l-5-5-5 5M12 3v12"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="drop-title">PDF 파일을 끌어다 놓거나 클릭</div>
    <div class="drop-sub">여러 파일 동시 선택 가능</div>
    <div class="drop-formats">
      <span class="format-pill">.pdf</span>
      <span class="format-pill">다중 선택</span>
      <span class="format-pill">무제한</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Uploaded Files -->
  <div id="uploadedSection" style="display:none">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-label">업로드된 파일</span>
      <span class="file-count" id="fileCount">0개</span>
    </div>
    <div class="thumb-grid" id="thumbGrid"></div>

    <div class="action-bar">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" id="analyzeBtn" onclick="analyze()">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
        AI 자동 분류 및 병합
      </button>
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="addMoreFiles()">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"/></svg>
        파일 추가
      </button>
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="clearAll()">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
        초기화
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Result -->
  <div id="resultSection" style="display:none">

    <div class="status-bar" id="statusBar">
      <div class="status-dot" id="statusDot"></div>
      <div class="status-text" id="statusText">대기 중</div>
      <div class="status-progress" id="statusProgress"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="progress-track" id="progressTrack" style="display:none">
      <div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill" style="width:0%"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="groups-container" id="groupsContainer"></div>

    <div class="download-section" id="downloadSection" style="display:none">
      <div class="download-info">
        <div class="download-title">병합 준비 완료</div>
        <div class="download-sub" id="downloadSub">그룹 순서대로 PDF가 병합됩니다</div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" id="mergeBtn" onclick="mergeAndDownload()">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3"/></svg>
        병합 PDF 다운로드
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  <p>파일은 브라우저에서만 처리됩니다 · 서버 업로드 없음 · <a href="https://makewon.com" target="_blank">메이크창고</a></p>
  <p style="margin-top:.5rem">&copy; 2025 Makemine Design. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

